  "levels": [
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxx",
        "x>----gx",
        "x------x",
        "xP-----x",
        "xxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "The wind-up robot marches one step forward every time you spend a turn. You are the blue 'P'. You cannot touch the robot, and you do not need to: press z to wait and watch it dock on 'g'.",
      "minMoves": 5,
      "title": "Wind-Up"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxx",
        "x>----x",
        "x-----x",
        "xP---gx",
        "xxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "When the robot cannot step forward, it does not stop. It spends the turn rotating clockwise, then marches on. Its whole life is march-or-turn.",
      "minMoves": 7,
      "title": "Clockwise"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x-------x",
        "x->-----x",
        "x-------x",
        "x---g---x",
        "x------Px",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "You are a wall too. Stand in the robot's path at the right moment and it will turn clockwise toward the pad.",
      "minMoves": 12,
      "title": "Body Check"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x>------x",
        "x---c---x",
        "x---P---x",
        "x--g----x",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "Crates 'c' push like furniture, one cell at a time. A crate in the road turns the robot just like your body does. Unlike your body, it stays put.",
      "minMoves": 6,
      "title": "Roadblock"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x>---o--x",
        "x---P---x",
        "x--g----x",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "Pits 'o' do not stop the robot. It will march straight in and wreck itself. This one has four turns to live.",
      "minMoves": 5,
      "title": "Sinkhole"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x>--o--gx",
        "x---c---x",
        "x---P---x",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "A crate pushed into a pit fills it and leaves solid floor.",
      "minMoves": 6,
      "title": "Landfill"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>-----o-x",
        "x-----P--x",
        "x--xgx---x",
        "x---xx---x",
        "x--------x",
        "xxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "The dock only opens from the north, and the pit is waiting. There is exactly one place to stand.",
      "minMoves": 6,
      "title": "Needle"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x>------x",
        "x--xx---x",
        "x--xg---x",
        "x--xx---x",
        "xP------x",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "The pen opens from the east, so the robot must arrive walking west. Let the walls make the first turns for you.",
      "minMoves": 13,
      "title": "Sheep Pen"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>-----o-x",
        "x----x-c-x",
        "x---xg---x",
        "x----x---x",
        "x-----P--x",
        "xxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "First save it, then catch it. The crate plugs the pit, and the dock takes deliveries from the east only.",
      "minMoves": 14,
      "title": "Terminal"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>-------x",
        "x--------x",
        "x--xxg-x-x",
        "x---xxx--x",
        "x---P----x",
        "xxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "No pits and no crates: just you, the robot, and a lap of the yard. If you cannot get there in time, send the robot the long way around.",
      "minMoves": 25,
      "title": "Roundabout"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>--------x",
        "x-xx-xxxx-x",
        "x-x-----x-x",
        "x-x-xgx-x-x",
        "x-x-----x-x",
        "x-xxxxxxx-x",
        "x---P-----x",
        "xxxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "The core is two rings deep. Meeting the robot head-on bounces it backward, and you will need the lap that buys. Once you are both inside, remember: in a narrow ring, whoever is in front decides where the other one turns.",
      "minMoves": 34,
      "title": "Snail"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x--xx---x",
        "x-x----ox",
        "x-x-<x--x",
        "x---x---x",
        "x--gx--Px",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "The robot circles its cage clockwise and slips out the east gap, straight into the pit. Redirecting it means getting into the cage with it, and living on its rhythm.",
      "minMoves": 16,
      "title": "Escapement"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>------ox",
        "x--c-----x",
        "x--P---xgx",
        "x------x-x",
        "x--------x",
        "xxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "One crate, one pit, one dock. Remember that you, the robot, and a crate you keep pushing all move at exactly the same speed.",
      "minMoves": 16,
      "title": "Convoy"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>------xxx",
        "xxxxxx-xgxx",
        "xxxxxx-xPxx",
        "xxxxxx---xx",
        "xxxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "Every wall turns the robot right for free. A left turn is three rights, and the third only happens if you are standing right where it came from. Stay close behind, and mind the shuttle upstairs.",
      "minMoves": 35,
      "title": "Heel"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxxxxx",
        "x>------Pxxx",
        "xxxxxx-xxxxx",
        "xxxxxx-xxxxx",
        "xxxxxx-co-gx",
        "xxxxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "Last delivery of the night. Plug the floor before you invite it downstairs, and do not get caught in the hall when it comes marching back.",
      "minMoves": 26,
      "title": "Night Shift"
    },
    {
      "board": [
        "xxxxxxxxx",
        "x-------x",
        "x-----W-x",
        "x-------x",
        "x---h---x",
        "xP------x",
        "xxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "A new model walks the floor tonight: the violet robot turns COUNTERclockwise when blocked, and docks only on violet pads 'h'. Everything you know still works. Backwards.",
      "goals": [
        [
          "H"
        ]
      ],
      "minMoves": 12,
      "title": "Widdershins"
    },
    {
      "board": [
